  other noteworthy musical tevyes have included luther adler , herschel bernardi , paul lipson ( original broadway run over 2,000 performances ) , shmuel rudenski ( original israeli yiddish and german productions ) , alfred molina ( 2004 broadway revival ) , harvey fierstein and henry goodman .

characters in musicals : as a child in the ' 60s , pia zadora played tevye 's daughter bielke in this broadway musical

